Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.08,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Yeah, right!}À rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.26,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You were clearly pointing\Nat the second choice!}Rõ ràng là cậu chỉ vào đồng!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.44,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Lies and slander.}Dối trá và vu khống.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Try to be a little less obvious!}Mắt cậu đang cười kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.52,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,милашка. Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{What was that?}Nói gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:18.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I called you stupid.}Đồ ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.36,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,милашка. Dễ thương
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.41,flashbacktop,ALYA,0,0,0,,{милашка.}Kawaii
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.41,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H394045&\c&HE5F0EB&}{You cutie, you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.98,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{What do you }{\i0}{mean}{\i1}{, cutie?!}Dễ thương là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.77,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You said that before, too!}Cậu nói lúc nãy rồi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:35.15,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I can understand you, you know!}Tớ có thể hiểu đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.92,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H394045&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Look at you. You're red as a baby.}Nhìn mặt cậu đỏ lên kìa, cứ như đứa trẻ ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.61,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Who're you calling a baby? You little...}Cậu gọi là là đứa trẻ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.25,sign_generic,TITLECARD1,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HEAFCFA&\3c&HB590F8&\an7\frz11.4\fs35\fade(200,1)\move(103.091,158.364,103,153.273)}{Sometimes}
