Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.59,sign_generic,TITLECARD,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs25\b1\bord0\c&H2E404D&\an8}{Alya }{\fnArial\bord2\3c&H9A6BEE&\c&HFBF7FF&\fs}{Sometimes }{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\bord0\c&H2E404D&\fs25}{Hides\NHer Feelings in Russian}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:21.44,italicstop,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{As a kid, I often played with a Russian girl \Nwho lived near my grandpa's place.}Hồi còn nhỏ, mình hay chơi với một \Ncô bé người Nga sống gần nhà bà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:20.81,sign_generic,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,{\fs14\frz6.763\c&HFBE2FF&\3c&H9B48F4&\b1\pos(144,314.364)\fade(1,450)}{Episode 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:20.81,sign_generic,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,{\bord1\shad1\an7\pos(194,281.273)\3c&H828081&\4c&H636162&\blur1\fade(400,450)}{Alya Hides Her Feelings in Russian}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.78,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I must've picked it up then.}Lúc đó thành ra tự nhớ luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.02,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{And I can still pretty much \Nunderstand spoken Russian.}Và mình vẫn có thể hiểu được tiếng Nga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:32.45,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{But who woulda thought \Nit'd lead to this bizarre situation?}Nhưng ai ngờ lại dẫn đến cái tình huống này chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:39.75,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{This cute Russian girl next to me fawns \Nover me exclusively in Russian, and I know!}Người đẹp Nga dễ thương bên cạnh\N đang nịnh nọt mình bằng tiếng Nga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.71,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{If I came out and admitted it now...}Nếu thừa nhận mình biết tiếng Nga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.03,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Nope, not happening.}Không, không có gi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:59.14,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Outside of emergencies and cases \Nwhere they're needed for reference,}Ngoài trường hợp khẩn cấp và cần tham khảo,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.94,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{the use of mobile phones \Nis banned within school grounds.}thì điện thoại bị cấm ở trường nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Which means this is allowed, \Nbecause this is an emergency.}Tức là được, vì đây là tình huống khẩn cấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:09.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I'm going to ask you against \Nmy better judgment: how, exactly?}Để hỏi lại chứ khẩn cấp chỗ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Free rolls end in ten minutes.}Quay miễn phí sẽ kết thúc trong 10 phút nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.87,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You have some nerve, pulling this stunt \Nbeside a student council officer.}Cậu dám làm trò trước mặt thành viên hội học sinh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:20.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Let's go! SSR Tsukuyomi is mine!}Quá ngon! SSR Tsukiyomi ra rồi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.74,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I'm taking that!}Đưa đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:22.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:28.51,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Tsukuyomi? Like, the goddess \Nof the moon in Japanese mythology?}Tsukuyomi? Nữ thần mặt trăng của Nhật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.88,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Why is her hair silver and not jet black?}Tại sao lại tóc trắng mà không phải đen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Who knows? Probably a nod to the moon.}Ai biết? Chắc theo màu mặt trăng?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:37.14,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Who cares about that, anyway? She's cute.}Ai quan tâm chứ. Dễ thương là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You are too kind, milady!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Man, I really rolled Tsukuyomi-sama.}Chà, đúng là Tsukuyomi-sama rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:50.36,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H292D28&\c&HE5F0EB&}{I have silver hair too, you know... You cheater.}Tớ cũng có tóc bạc nữa nè... tên phản bội
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Uh, what was that?}Cậu nói gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.37,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I called you a game junkie.}Tôi nói cậu là tên nghiện game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hey, them's fighting words.}Này, tớ không thích thế đâu nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.03,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?}H-Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:05.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You can't call me a junkie when I'm F2P.}Cậu gọi tớ nghiện khi tớ là F2P.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That's an affront to \Nthe true junkies: the P2W whales.}Là sự sỉ nhục với những kẻ nghiện thực thụ: P2W.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:16.52,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You make a good point. Nobody would \Nwant to be put in the same category as you.}Phải nhỉ, không ai muốn xếp chung hạng với cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Savage!}Ác quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.21,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{And here I thought you actually looked \Nserious and committed for once.}Mãi mới thấy cậu nghiêm túc nói chuyện vậy mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:27.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Now, now. Commitment is my middle name, \Nand that's an understatement.}Này này, tớ lúc nào cũng nghiêm túc cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.64,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{It's the overstatement of the century.}Đó là lời nói dối của thế kỉ đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You do realize we have \Nanother 80 years to go?}Nhưng thế kỉ này mới có hơn 20 năm mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.62,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Muốn nổi tiếng!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.58,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{What are you eating, Masachika?}Cậu ăn gì thế Masachika?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Super spicy mapo ramen.}Mì siêu cay Mapo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.08,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Hey! Don't ignore my soulful plea!}Này, đừng có phớt lờ tớ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.10,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{I figured it was \Njust the usual outburst.}Tớ nghĩ đó chỉ là câu nói bộc phát thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.63,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Oh, great. Check out Mr. Hot Stuff over here.}Tớ ghét mấy tên đào hoa là vậy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.72,Default,BOY,0,0,0,,{Look, it's the student council!}Nhìn kìa, là hội học sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:59.15,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord1.4\3c&H202928&\c&HE5F0EB&\pos(320,270)\fade(1,400)}{Alisa Mikhailovna Kujo\NStudent Council Treasurer}Alisa Mikhailovna Kujo\N Thủ quỹ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:58.25,top,ALYA,0,0,0,,{We got here late. Are there any seats open?}Chúng ta đến trễ quá, còn chỗ trống không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:04.60,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord1.4\3c&H202928&\c&HE5F0EB&\pos(320,270)\fade(300,300)}{Mariya Mikhailovna Kujo\NStudent Council Secretary}Mariya Mikhailovna Kujo\N Thư kí
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:04.44,top,MARIYA,0,0,0,,{It's okay. I'll eat over there \Nwith my classmates.}Không sao. Chị sẽ ăn cùng bạn mình ở kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:08.48,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord1.4\3c&H202928&\c&HE5F0EB&\pos(320,270)\fade(300,1)}{Suou Yuki\NStudent Council Spokesperson}Suou Yuki\N Người phát ngôn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.01,top,YUKI,0,0,0,,{Thank you for your\Nconsideration, Masha-senpai.}Cảm ơn chị nhé, chị Masha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:12.41,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{The Kujo sisters are both so pretty.}Chị em nhà Kujo đúng là xinh đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:17.20,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Kujo-senpai is so pretty. \NI'd love to get to know all about her.}Sướng ghê, tớ muốn được gần gũi với chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:20.48,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{I hear she's got a boyfriend, though.}Nhưng nghe nói chị ấy có bạn trai đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.12,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Huh.}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:27.12,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{She keeps turning down boys who ask her out, \Nsaying she's already dating someone.}Chị ấy lúc nào cũng từ chối đám\N con trai và nói đã có người hẹn hò.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:30.53,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Taken or not, Takeshi's still got no shot.}Dù có hay không thì thằng Takeshi \Ncũng không có cửa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:34.87,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Shut it! Don't get a big head \Njust 'cause you're friends with Lady Alya!}Im mồm! Đừng có tỏ vẻ khi chú\N mày quen nữ thần Alya nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.46,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Guh, I hate you.}Đáng ghét mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:42.43,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{How come you get to address \Nthat ice queen with her nickname?}Sao chỉ có mày là được nữ hoàng băng giá gọi tên?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{It's cool, I guess.}Tại tao ngầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.77,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{But she does keep snapping at me.}Nhưng cậu ta lúc nào cũng chọc tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.44,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Hey, it's better than getting no response.}Còn hơn là bị bơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.29,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{She basically never talks to anyone else.}Cậu ấy hầu như chẳng nói chuyện với ai cả
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:57.29,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Guess that's what sitting next to her \Nfor more than a year gets you.}Có khi tớ ngồi cạnh cậu ta hơn cả năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:01.64,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{If I had to shoot my shot with one \Nof those three, it'd have to be Suou-san.}Quả nhiên nếu phải chọn thì Suou nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:05.70,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{She's approachable, unlike Lady Alya, \Nso it feels like she's gettable!}Vui vẻ hoà đồng, ngược với nữ hoàng Alya luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.67,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Not that she isn't out of \Nmost guys' league, of course.}Và tất nhiên luôn nằm trong danh\N sách được con trai yêu thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:14.57,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is}{\i0}{ she gettable, though? Apparently \Nshe's turned down more guys than Kujo-san.}Nghe nói cậu ấy từ chối còn nhiều hơn Kujo nữa đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.32,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{That's the problem.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.49,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{She is a rich girl, so maybe she's \Nalready been promised to someone?}Vì là tiểu thư nên hẳn là có hôn phu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.93,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{You know anything, Masachika?}Cậu biết gì không, Masachika?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Why ask me?}Sao lại hỏi tớ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.47,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Isn't that obvious?}Còn hỏi nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:41.24,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{May I sit here, Masachika-kun?}Tớ ngồi đây nhé Masachika?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Sure, go ahead.}Cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You guys okay with that?}Tụi bay cũng ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.24,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Y-Y-Yeah.}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.77,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{Totally.}Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.46,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{Thank you kindly.}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:56.46,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{I see you ordered \Nthe same thing, Masachika-kun.}Cậu cũng gọi món giống tớ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:11:00.16,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{It's surprising that you have \Na taste for that stuff too, Suou-san.}Cậu ăn hết được hả, Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.06,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{Oh, you needn't be so formal.}Không cần trang trọng đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.60,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{We're in the same year.}Chúng ta học cùng năm mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.85,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Well, if you say so.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.82,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{And yes, of course I eat ramen.}Và dĩ nhiên tớ có thể ăn hết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:14.06,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{I often go out to eat some on days off.}Ngày nghỉ hay ăn ở ngoài lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.61,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{W-Wow.}V-Vậy hả.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:27.56,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{This is lovely, though I do think \Nit could stand to be a bit spicier.}Ngon ghê. Cơ mà phải cay hơn thì tuyệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.50,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Right?}Nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wish we could top it with some chili oil.}Có thêm sa tế thì hay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:35.88,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{It might be a good idea to \Nbring it up with the student council.}Hay lần tới dùng quyền\N lực hội học sinh đưa nó vào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Don't bring your personal preferences\N into admin matters.}Đừng có lợi dụng công việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:40.20,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{I was simply joking.}Tớ đùa thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Are you two friends?}Hai cậu là bạn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:47.66,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{We've known each other since we were kids.}Bọn tớ biết nhau từ bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.22,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You have?}Vậy hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.98,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{Indeed. We've gone to school together \Nall the way from preschool to now.}Ừm, đi học chung với nhau từ mẫu giáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.99,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.04,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Actually, are you two friends?}Cơ mà hai cậu thân nhau hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:01.78,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{I suppose you could say it's a process.}Tớ muốn nói thế nhưng đang trong quá trình.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:07.05,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{If nothing else, I do want \Nto be friends with Alisa-san.}Nếu ổn thì tớ muốn làm bạn với Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:11.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I don't think being friends \Nwith me will be any fun.}Tớ nghĩ không vui khi kết bạn với tớ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:18.38,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{So, you aren't entirely opposed to the idea?}Tức là cậu không ghét điều đó nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I guess not.}Ừm, không...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:26.04,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{Well, we're done here.}Bọn này ăn xong rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.64,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{See you.}Vậy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Okay?}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.39,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,{They're too shiny for me. I can't!}Họ toả sáng quá chịu không nổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.27,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{By the way...}Cơ mà này...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:44.51,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{Masachika-kun, have you considered \Nmy offer to join the student council?}Masachika, có định quay lại hội học sinh không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:47.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Like I've said over and over, \NI'm not interested.}Đã nói rồi, không hứng thú.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:52.45,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{I think you would be a great fit \Nwith Alisa-san and myself.}Nếu là cậu thì sẽ hoà hợp với bọn tớ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.50,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{And what's more,}Và hơn nữa,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.95,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{you have experience as \Nstudent council vice president.}cậu cũng từng làm hội phó còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:56.67,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:02.82,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{When we were in middle school, \NI was president and he was vice president.}Hồi học cấp 2, tớ là hội trưởng và cậu ấy hội phó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.55,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I only ran because Yuki asked me to.}Tớ chỉ làm do Yuki năn nỉ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:13.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Elections at our school required \Neach candidate to have a running mate.}Do tranh cử phải yêu cầu có 2 người.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.34,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{It may come as a surprise to you,}Tuy có ngạc nhiên với cậu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:21.78,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{but he }{\i1}{is}{\i0}{ capable of getting \Nthings done, believe it or not.}nhưng cậu ấy rất giỏi hoàn thành công việc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.07,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Uh, "believe it or not"?}Ngạc nhiên là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.07,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Ai biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.95,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H292D28&\c&HE5F0EB&}{You don't have to tell me. I know that already.}Không cần nói, tớ biết rồi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.58,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\fade(250,1)\blur1\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H162734&\pos(316.364,90.364)}{Oshiruko}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.01,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{So, you two are close, huh?}Hai cậu thân thiết quá nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:37.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Surprised?}Ngạc nhiên à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.69,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I very much am.}Ừm, ngạc nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.68,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I never imagined that any girl \Nwould want to be friends with you.}Không ngờ cậu lại có bạn nữ giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Huh? Excuse me?}Hả? Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:45.97,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What?}Gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.59,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Uh, I just mean...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{There's one right here?}Cậu cũng là nữ giới mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.85,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Wait, are we friends?}Khoan, chúng ta là bạn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Huh? Are we not?}Hả? Chứ không à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.35,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{No, you're right. We are friends.}Không, chúng ta là bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.95,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hey, where are you going?}Này, cậu đi đâu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:05.37,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I remembered something \NI had to do at the student council office.}Có việc cần làm ở hội học sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{What's with her?}Cậu ta bị gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.08,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1D2520&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H2C393B&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Masachka!}Masachka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.46,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Again, it's Masachika.}Masachika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:26.59,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H36383E&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Hehe.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.72,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H2B3226&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Come up here, Masachka!}Lại đây nào Masachka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.23,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H2C3338&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Look at this beautiful sunset.}Nhìn kìa, hoàng hôn đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.60,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H303633&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Yeah, it's very p... p...}Ừm, nó rất đ- đe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.73,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H292D28&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Pretty.}Đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.15,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H292D28&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Very pretty.}Rất đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.00,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H192021&\c&HE5F0EB&}{See you tomorrow, Masachka.}Gặp sau nhé, Masachka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.25,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1A2427&\c&HE5F0EB&}{Yeah, see you.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:13.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I studied Russian like crazy \Nbecause I wanted to talk to her,}Mình đã học tiếng nga\N như điên để nói chuyện với cậu ấy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{but I don't even remember her name.}nhưng chẳng nhớ nổi tên luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.02,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Top of the morning to you!}Chào buổi sáng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.27,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(286.545,160.182)\bord0\b1\c&H9D8262&}{Day Duty:\N Kujo/Kuze}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.27,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(286.545,160.182)\bord0\b1\c&H9D8262&}{Day Duty:\N Kujo/Kuze}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:39.37,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Perfect, if I do say so myself.}Hoàn hảo! Ta mà đã ra tay thì chỉ thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hey, morning.}Chào cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.78,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Morning, Kuze-kun.}Chào cậu, Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:48.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I woke up real early this morning}Tớ dậy sớm sáng nay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.63,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{and had nothing to do, \Nso I came in early and took care of some things.}và rảnh quá nên dọn dẹp luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.85,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You? Waking up early?}Cậu? Dậy sớm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.07,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Hell must've frozen over.}Hôm nay có tuyết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:59.39,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{You sure do know \Nhow to pick the most biting remarks.}Cậu đúng là thích phá không khí ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:04.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I'll wipe the blackboard in the morning.}Tôi sẽ lau bảng buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:05.39,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Deal.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{What happened there? \NDid you step in a puddle or something?}Gì kia? Cậu đạp vào bãi nước à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.61,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{No. I'm not like you.}Không. Ai mà ngốc như cậu chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.49,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Are you implying I'm a chronic spacer-outer?}Ý cậu ám chỉ tớ là kẻ hay thơ thẩn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.66,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Rest assured, I wasn't.}Không ai nói thế cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:23.72,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{A truck splash-and-dashed me on the way here.}Đang đi học thì bị xe tải té nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, way to put a damper on things.}Đúng là xui ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:30.89,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Well, it was partly my fault \Nfor walking so close to the road.}Nói chung cũng tại tôi khi đi gần đường.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:34.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{And I have some spare socks, so I'll live.}Lúc nãy có ghé cửa hàng mua vớ thay thế rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.28,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Kuze-kun.}Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:42.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{You were a student council officer \Nwith Suou-san in middle school, right?}Hồi cấp 2 cậu từng làm trong hội học sinh nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Hmm? Yeah, I was.}Hả? À ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.00,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Huh.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:49.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Say, Kuze-kun.}Nè Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Yeah?}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.69,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Are you not willing to be \Npart of the student council?}Cậu không định vào lại hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Not you, too.}Cậu cũng nói thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:55.70,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Answer me.}Trả lời đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:17:00.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I'm not interested in joining.}Ừm, tớ không có hứng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.70,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{But what if I...}Nhưng nếu tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Nothing. Never mind.}Không. Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:28.40,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Hey, could you grab a spare sock \Nfor me from my locker?}Nè, cậu ra tủ của tôi lấy vớ được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:29.36,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wha?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:33.14,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I can't go get it myself \Nnow that I've taken it off.}Tháo ra rồi sao mà đi được?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Get to it.}Mau lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Fine.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:41.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{I'm opening it.}Tớ mở ra nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:45.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.73,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Put it on for me.}Mang vào luôn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wha?!}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:49.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Do you have to ask? \NWhat's wrong with }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{?!}À không! Cậu bị gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.52,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{As thanks for grabbing my sock for me.}Lời cảm ơn vì đã lấy vớ cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.72,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{It would be a nice little treat for you, no?}Với cậu là phần thưởng còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{That only holds true for a small set \Nof people with peculiar taste.}Điều đó chỉ đúng với những người \Ncó sở thích đặc biệt thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Oh, am I wrong?}Thế không phải à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:03.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Nope! Very much a treat!}Không! Quá đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.39,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H363228&\c&HE5F0EB&}{It is for me, too.}Tớ cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.03,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Y'know, I've been wondering.}Lúc trước mình đã tò mò...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.05,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Why are her displays of affection \Nfor me in Russian so weird?}Sao nhỏ này thể hiện tình cảm bằng tiếng Nga với mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:18.24,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Maybe her perfectionism in playing \Nher ideal self is stressing her out,}Có lẽ việc thể hiện cảm xúc bản thân\N khiến cậu ta bị căng thẳng,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:22.34,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,nên dùng mình để giải toả?{and she's using me as a release or something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.62,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{So she's mentally exposing herself...}Tức là cậu ta bộc lộ cảm xúc...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.25,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Wait, she's an exhibitionist?}Khoan, thích phô trương hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{What?}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Oh, just thinking about what you said.}À, đang tò mò về những gì cậu nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.66,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Not much.}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.75,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{I just called you a coward.}Chỉ là đang gọi cậu hèn nhát thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:38.01,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Forget it. I'll put it on myself.}Kệ đi, tôi tự đeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,{Nah, no need for that.}Không cần đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.16,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,{Hey, wait! Wh-What are you doing?!}Này! C-Cậu làm gì thế?
